Week 3 – Data Transformation & Interactive Data Cleaning Session

Topics Covered:

In the third week, we focused on transforming data using various tools available in Power Query. Data transformation helps convert raw and inconsistent data into a structured format suitable for analysis.

Transformation Techniques Learned:

->Split Column

->Merge Column

->Extract values from columns

->Trim and Clean text

->Formatting text values

->Converting text data into numeric values

->Changing column data types

Example Transformations:

->Splitting full names into first name and last name

->Removing unwanted text from numeric columns

->Formatting percentage values

->Standardizing inconsistent entries

Interactive Data Cleaning Session:

During this week we also had an interactive learning session. One of our team members performed data cleaning on a dataset while the rest of the team actively participated by suggesting steps and discussing the best ways to clean and transform the data.

This collaborative session helped us better understand practical data cleaning techniques and how different Power Query tools can be applied in real-world datasets.

Learning Outcome:

This week helped us understand how to transform and prepare data effectively. The interactive session also improved our practical understanding of data cleaning and teamwork in solving data preparation problems.
